    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 guidance. The validation comparison against the clinical observational dataset demonstrates RHI agreement within ±12%, satisfying the output comparison acceptance criterion. The assessment team concluded that the CFD model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU. Decision: Accepted.",
